title: Silent Letter Words
details: Silent Letter Words skill for Alexa lets you know different words in English with silent letters. For example, 'debt', here 'b' is silent.You can listen to words with silent letters randomly or words with a specific silent letter.How to Use:1. Ask Alexa to open this skill by using any one of the following example phrases:   "Alexa, open Silent Letter Words" or,   "Alexa, start Silent Letter Words" or,   "Alexa, launch Silent Letter Words"2. Once in, the skill will ask you if you want to know words with silent letters randomly or words with specific silent letter.3. You can choose to listen randomly or listen to words with specific silent letter.   If you choose to listen to words with specific silent letter, it will ask you a letter. Tell Alexa a letter and she will tell you the words with that silent letter.

title: Silent letter words
details: Silent letter words is a skill to help you learn about various silent letter words which exist in the English language. Many people find it difficult to understand words which have silent letters in them, so this skill helps them to find out silent letter words randomly or find silent letter words by a specific letter. For ex : 'c' in "Acquire", 'n' in "Autumn", etc. You can say:"Alexa, open Silent letter words""Alexa, start Silent letter words""Alexa, launch Silent letter words"Please leave a 5-star review if you love this skill, or send us an email with your suggestions at info@cofinite.in .
